    "body": "https://neovim.io/doc/user/deprecated/ Generated at 2026-05-06 15:25 from [27e7aba](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/commit/27e7aba9821eb8a4a92bf4abd0af099b88b0735d)\n\n<img width=\"1236\" height=\"1161\" alt=\"https://neovim.io/doc/user/deprecated/#_api\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/648b6359-0853-4878-a9a2-520454f4c7f4\" />\n\nTOC at right is rendered as\n\n- Deprecated Features\n  - Deprecated in 0.13\n  - Api\n  - Events\n  - Lua\n  - Deprecated in 0.12\n  - Api\n  - Diagnostics\n  - Highlights\n\nI would like to suggest structuring like\n\n- Deprecated Features\n  - Deprecated in 0.13\n    - Api\n    - Events\n    - Lua\n  - Deprecated in 0.12\n    - Api\n    - Diagnostics\n    - Highlights\n\nPlus, all the API headings in versions from 0.8− to 0.13 have id of [`_api`](https://neovim.io/doc/user/deprecated/#_api), therefore \"Api\" under e.g. \"Deprecated in 0.10\" navigates to that in 0.13.",
